22
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:42,910
Don't be nervous.

23
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:43,510
Be normal？

24
00:03:43,510 --> 00:03:45,110
Be normal. Don't be nervous.

25
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:02,650
