It's okay.

48
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:30,180
It's fine.

49
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:32,330
We're all here. It's fine.

50
00:06:59,020 --> 00:07:00,190
Supermarket delivery.

51
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:01,720
I left the stuff at the door.

52
00:07:09,580 --> 00:07:10,220
Don't run.

53
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:11,340
It's okay, don't run.

54
00:07:11,340 --> 00:07:11,990
Slow down.

55
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:13,780
Go. Go. Go.

56
00:07:13,990 --> 00:07:14,700
Go on.

57
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:08,340
Quan.

58
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:11,340
