73
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:49,580
Room 802.

74
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:50,980
Give it to me.
I'll deliver it for you later.

75
00:09:50,980 --> 00:09:51,700
No way.

76
00:09:51,700 --> 00:09:52,580
It's almost late.

77
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:53,670
I'll get fined.

78
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:55,670
A delivery guy is going to
the eighth floor.

79
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:56,460
