81
00:09:57,460 --> 00:09:58,340
Stop talking.

82
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:02,920
Okay.

83
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:04,950
Let him deliver it.

84
00:10:05,340 --> 00:10:06,820
Stay on the eighth floor
and don't come down.

85
00:10:06,820 --> 00:10:07,620
Go to the eighth floor.

86
00:10:07,620 --> 00:10:08,310
Don't look up.

87
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:10,970
Once you deliver it,
don't come down instantly.

88
00:10:31,340 --> 00:10:34,140
I'll disguise myself as a delivery guy
to meet you.

89
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,220
They're not opening up.

90
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:54,950
Should we break in? Let's do it.

91
00:10:56,340 --> 00:10:57,700
Don't rush.

92
00:10:57,860 --> 00:10:59,640
We don't know the situation inside yet.

93
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:00,520
It's too risky.

94
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:01,550
Wait a bit longer.

95
00:11:12,070 --> 00:11:12,950
Bro,

96
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:14,940
