107
00:12:06,820 --> 00:12:07,750
Check the store.

108
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:09,390
Team 1, Team 1.

109
00:12:09,390 --> 00:12:10,320
What's going on?

110
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:13,170
Daquan jumped out the window.

111
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,270
Kai, handle this.

112
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:15,870
Jin Longzheng, come with me.

113
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:24,030
Stop!

114
00:12:25,980 --> 00:12:26,700
Freeze!

115
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:27,750
Don't run!

116
00:12:28,570 --> 00:12:29,380
Freeze!

117
00:12:33,250 --> 00:12:33,910
Don't move!

118
00:12:34,310 --> 00:12:34,820
Drop the knife!

119
00:12:34,820 --> 00:12:35,820
Get out!

120
00:12:35,820 --> 00:12:36,310
Drop the knife!

121
00:12:36,310 --> 00:12:36,740
Hurry!

122
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:37,270
Back off!

123
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,340
Back off!

124
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:40,070
Calm down.

125
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:41,430
Calm down.

126
00:12:42,580 --> 00:12:43,740
Daquan ran into a recycling station.

127
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:44,500
He's holding a hostage.

128
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:45,580
Shut up!

129
00:12:48,070 --> 00:12:48,700
Stay calm.

130
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:50,220
Please, let me go.

131
00:12:50,220 --> 00:12:51,270
Tell us what you want.

132
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:52,520
We can meet your demands, okay?

133
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:53,610
Drop your guns!

134
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,480
Okay.

135
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:56,580
Get me a car.

136
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:57,580
Get a car!

137
00:12:57,580 --> 00:12:58,100
Good.

138
00:13:02,310 --> 00:13:03,240
Tell your men to back off.

139
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,070
Back off!

140
00:13:04,090 --> 00:13:05,180
Okay, no problem.

141
00:13:07,310 --> 00:13:08,130
Where's the car?

142
00:13:08,130 --> 00:13:08,990
It's on the way.

143
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:09,950
Cut the crap!

144
00:13:13,620 --> 00:13:14,670
Call an ambulance!

145
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,730
Call an ambulance!

146
00:13:27,540 --> 00:13:28,660
Entered Room 701.

147
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:29,740
