165
00:14:46,430 --> 00:14:48,030
I've never even met Ding Lai.

166
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:49,910
Ding Lai lives with Daquan.

167
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:51,110
You didn't know that?

168
00:14:51,550 --> 00:14:52,150
Come down.

169
00:14:52,310 --> 00:14:52,670
Come down.

170
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:53,460
Come down.

171
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:54,150
Come down.

172
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:54,950
Don't.

173
00:14:57,300 --> 00:14:58,350
I heard from Quan

174
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:00,920
