175
00:15:01,070 --> 00:15:01,860
When?

176
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:03,820
Right about now.

177
00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:09,450
What do you mean by "now"?

178
00:15:11,950 --> 00:15:12,820
Now?

179
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:18,380
How many bags did that delivery guy have
when he went up?

180
00:15:19,070 --> 00:15:19,790
One.

181
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:24,340
When he came down,

182
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:25,670
