183
00:15:31,790 --> 00:15:32,380
Split up and chase him.

184
00:15:32,380 --> 00:15:32,910
Split up.

185
00:15:39,190 --> 00:15:39,790
Hello.

186
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:40,390
Police.

187
00:15:40,390 --> 00:15:41,550
Be gentle to my bike!

188
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:42,900
Pick it up at the PSB tomorrow.

189
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:43,570
Hu Wenjing.

190
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,250
Respond.

191
00:15:48,030 --> 00:15:48,910
Jin? Jin?

192
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:52,910
Find a way to contact them immediately.

193
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:53,950
Be ready to provide backup.

194
00:15:53,950 --> 00:15:54,790
Okay.

195
00:16:08,820 --> 00:16:09,700
Do you hear me?

196
00:16:10,220 --> 00:16:11,100
Jin Longzheng?

197
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:54,540
Ding Lai.

198
00:16:55,950 --> 00:16:56,550
What's up?

199
00:16:56,700 --> 00:16:57,190
I am police.

200
00:16:57,190 --> 00:16:58,650
Please take off your mask.

201
00:17:00,500 --> 00:17:01,310
Sorry.

202
00:17:09,190 --> 00:17:10,220
I can tell you that

203
00:17:10,670 --> 00:17:13,109
we've been watching Han Qiang
for a long time.

204
00:17:13,109 --> 00:17:14,280
He has caused

205
00:17:14,390 --> 00:17:16,790
a loss of over two million yuan
to the Group.

206
00:17:17,190 --> 00:17:18,950
But since he admitted his mistake,

207
00:17:18,950 --> 00:17:21,130
we decided to keep him on probation

208
00:17:21,780 --> 00:17:23,710
and not hand him over to the police.

209
00:17:24,109 --> 00:17:25,369
Over two million yuan?

210
00:17:26,109 --> 00:17:27,250
It has nothing to do with me.

211
00:17:27,250 --> 00:17:27,859
I...

212
00:17:28,810 --> 00:17:29,260
I remember now.

213
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:30,220
I reimbursed him

214
00:17:30,220 --> 00:17:31,630
