216
00:17:34,190 --> 00:17:35,150
Just that one.

217
00:17:35,150 --> 00:17:36,010
That's enough.

218
00:17:36,220 --> 00:17:37,480
Show him the evidence.

219
00:18:01,670 --> 00:18:02,460
This

220
00:18:02,910 --> 00:18:04,310
