225
00:18:11,440 --> 00:18:13,240
Don't come to work tomorrow.

226
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:15,500
Go back to your department

227
00:18:16,140 --> 00:18:17,870
and settle your severance pay.

228
00:18:19,910 --> 00:18:21,710
I just filed one invoice for him.

229
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:23,980
I'm fired just because of this?

230
00:18:23,980 --> 00:18:25,640
We're just here to notify you.

231
00:18:25,980 --> 00:18:27,040
Do not make a scene.

232
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:28,760
Or we'll call the police.

233
00:18:29,260 --> 00:18:30,190
It's up to you.

234
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:31,670
Think about it.

235
00:18:38,950 --> 00:18:41,190
Please, can you give me a chance?

236
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:42,620
I only did it this once.

237
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,430
I just took a sum of money.

238
00:18:43,430 --> 00:18:44,630
I can pay it back.

239
00:18:44,630 --> 00:18:46,160
Let's just call the police.

240
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:55,180
No!

241
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:05,680
I'll leave.

242
00:19:06,330 --> 00:19:07,100
I'll leave.

243
00:19:59,210 --> 00:20:00,130
Ding Lai!

244
00:20:07,230 --> 00:20:07,840
Ding Lai!

245
00:20:53,350 --> 00:20:53,980
Ding Lai!

246
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:55,630
Ding Lai, stop!

247
00:20:56,300 --> 00:20:57,260
Police!

248
00:20:59,060 --> 00:20:59,670
Stop!

249
00:21:06,860 --> 00:21:08,340
Stop or I'll shoot!

250
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:11,390
Warning shot!

251
00:21:17,220 --> 00:21:18,060
Ding Lai!

252
00:21:19,860 --> 00:21:20,590
Come out.

253
00:21:22,220 --> 00:21:24,020
Next time, it won't be a warning.

254
00:28:14,250 --> 00:28:15,110
Jin Longzheng!

255
00:28:33,590 --> 00:28:34,460
Jin Longzheng!

256
00:28:52,910 --> 00:28:54,180
Ding Lai!

257
00:29:19,790 --> 00:29:20,650
Jin Longzheng!

258
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:27,700
Don't move.

259
00:29:28,780 --> 00:29:29,780
He ran over there.

260
00:29:30,220 --> 00:29:30,870
Which way?

261
00:29:30,870 --> 00:29:31,540
That way.

262
00:29:32,270 --> 00:29:33,320
Go after him.

263
00:29:33,430 --> 00:29:34,430
No. No.

264
00:29:35,770 --> 00:29:36,830
Chase him!

265
00:29:36,830 --> 00:29:37,780
Leave me alone.

266
00:29:37,780 --> 00:29:39,220
You'll die if I leave you.

267
00:29:39,750 --> 00:29:40,670
Don't move.

268
00:29:41,950 --> 00:29:42,830
Don't move.

269
00:29:42,830 --> 00:29:43,740
Get him.

270
00:29:47,110 --> 00:29:47,740
It's okay.

271
00:29:48,420 --> 00:29:49,350
No more chasing.

272
00:29:50,190 --> 00:29:50,700
When you recover,

273
00:29:50,700 --> 00:29:52,110
