274
00:29:53,710 --> 00:29:54,710
Please.

275
00:29:55,130 --> 00:29:56,160
You go catch him.

276
00:29:56,900 --> 00:29:57,730
Catch him.

277
00:29:59,950 --> 00:30:00,300
Don't move.

278
00:30:00,300 --> 00:30:01,420
Take small breaths.

279
00:30:01,420 --> 00:30:02,280
Jin Longzheng,

280
00:30:02,500 --> 00:30:03,190
