284
00:30:07,830 --> 00:30:08,870
Hurry!

285
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:10,420
At our last position.

286
00:30:10,950 --> 00:30:11,670
Jin Longzheng is injured.

287
00:30:11,670 --> 00:30:12,350
Hurry!

288
00:30:12,940 --> 00:30:13,500
Okay.

289
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:21,420
Jin Longzheng,

290
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:22,110
don't fall asleep.

291
00:30:22,110 --> 00:30:22,970
Jin Longzheng?

292
00:30:23,060 --> 00:30:23,900
Jin Longzheng?

293
00:30:23,900 --> 00:30:24,690
Look at me.

294
00:30:24,980 --> 00:30:25,840
Jin Longzheng.

295
00:30:26,950 --> 00:30:28,020
It's okay.

296
00:30:28,350 --> 00:30:29,590
Jin Longzheng, don't fall asleep.

297
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:30,450
Jin Longzheng!

298
00:30:30,980 --> 00:30:31,840
Jin Longzheng!

299
00:31:16,530 --> 00:31:17,790
What's taking so long?

